        loading="lazy"
        class="w-full h-full"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 id="operation">Operation</h3>

  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8">
    <p>Fish oil centrifuges operate by using a high centrifugal force to affect the separation of the three phases of processed fish residue. These centrifuges separate Fish Oil, Fish Meal, and stick water from inedible fish processing residue. The fish residue consists of non-saleable fish parts such as skin, guts, heads, bones, offal, and fins.</p>
  </div>

